WEBVTT

00:00:06.820 --> 00:00:08.620
=Destiny of the General's Bride=

00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:12.020
=Episode 16=

00:00:23.519 --> 00:00:24.320
Brilliant.

00:00:25.280 --> 00:00:26.719
Truly brilliant.

00:00:28.440 --> 00:00:29.760
Giving up your own bedchamber,

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:33.640
for your husband
and a Princess to share.

00:00:34.119 --> 00:00:35.560
And you yourself

00:00:35.920 --> 00:00:39.039
ran off to Mochun Brothel,
of all places.

00:00:39.439 --> 00:00:41.560
I used to wonder.

00:00:42.039 --> 00:00:43.359
Why would my upright brother

00:00:44.039 --> 00:00:45.280
insist on marrying

00:00:45.280 --> 00:00:46.679
a courtesan like you?

00:00:47.399 --> 00:00:48.759
Turns out,

00:00:48.759 --> 00:00:50.840
he only wanted you
to do flesh trade for him.

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:53.920
The willows of Zhangtai
are graceful indeed.

00:00:54.719 --> 00:00:55.359
Well?

00:00:56.280 --> 00:00:57.759
Second Master, are you tempted too?

00:01:04.560 --> 00:01:05.719
Of course I'm tempted.

00:01:07.959 --> 00:01:08.640
What's wrong?

00:01:09.480 --> 00:01:10.280
Sister-in-law,

00:01:11.840 --> 00:01:14.159
would you introduce me
to one of your own sisters?

00:01:14.480 --> 00:01:16.319
What would you need them for?

00:01:17.200 --> 00:01:20.120
Am I not enough to serve you?

00:01:25.760 --> 00:01:26.560
Who are you?

00:01:26.760 --> 00:01:28.079
It's only been a short while,

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:30.719
and you have forgotten me already.

00:01:31.920 --> 00:01:34.040
You are Su Hua!

00:01:35.840 --> 00:01:37.760
Second Master, you tormented me so.

00:01:38.519 --> 00:01:40.159
You abandoned me in the wilderness,

00:01:40.519 --> 00:01:42.359
left me to be gnawed by insects.

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:44.760
I hate you!

00:01:52.599 --> 00:01:54.000
Second Master, wake up!

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:55.239
- I'm Xiao Lian.
- I'm Hua.

00:01:55.319 --> 00:01:55.920
I'm Miss Yu!

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:57.200
Do you remember me?

00:02:03.560 --> 00:02:05.040
And I thought he was tougher than this.

00:02:05.480 --> 00:02:07.560
He's just another coward.

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:09.479
The play isn't over yet.

00:02:09.639 --> 00:02:13.639
Second Master Xiao, you'd better
keep your eyes wide open from now on.

00:02:31.520 --> 00:02:34.120
General, did you sleep well last night?

00:02:35.759 --> 00:02:37.360
The Princess locked the door herself.

00:02:37.680 --> 00:02:38.879
I didn't come to you,

00:02:38.960 --> 00:02:40.319
but you could've rescued me.

00:02:41.439 --> 00:02:43.680
Prince Consort, you were
basking in joy last night.

00:02:43.840 --> 00:02:45.120
How would I dare disturb?

00:02:46.120 --> 00:02:47.479
You'll be the death of me.

00:02:48.719 --> 00:02:50.280
Good thing I was prepared.

00:02:50.560 --> 00:02:52.159
I let five rats loose in the room.

00:02:53.080 --> 00:02:54.759
The Princess was so scared
she stayed up all night.

00:02:55.080 --> 00:02:56.719
She was too shaken to bother me.

00:02:59.360 --> 00:03:00.080
Really?

00:03:01.120 --> 00:03:02.039
Take a sniff if you want.

00:03:02.360 --> 00:03:04.120
Do I carry the scent of her powder?

00:03:09.080 --> 00:03:10.240
If that's the case,

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:12.639
then I have two more tasks

00:03:13.400 --> 00:03:15.520
I need you to help me with.

00:03:16.759 --> 00:03:17.560
Which two?

00:03:20.159 --> 00:03:21.240
First,

00:03:22.439 --> 00:03:24.400
I need a few tools for disguise.

00:03:24.719 --> 00:03:26.159
Since you are here,

00:03:26.319 --> 00:03:28.599
go and purchase them for me.

00:03:29.319 --> 00:03:31.120
That's easy. What's the other?

00:03:31.560 --> 00:03:32.800
Second,

00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:34.639
you'll have to stay there
one more night.

00:03:40.520 --> 00:03:41.360
I promise,

00:03:42.240 --> 00:03:43.919
after tomorrow when the play ends,

00:03:44.840 --> 00:03:46.680
I will never push you away again.

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:14.039
Su Hua has returned.

00:04:14.680 --> 00:04:15.719
Su Hua has returned!

00:04:19.720 --> 00:04:20.800
Mother!

00:04:21.360 --> 00:04:21.959
That woman...

00:04:22.360 --> 00:04:23.439
She is a ghost!

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:24.839
Seize her now!

00:04:24.959 --> 00:04:25.879
Seize her!

00:04:25.879 --> 00:04:27.399
What nonsense are you spewing?

00:04:27.639 --> 00:04:28.160
She is...

00:04:28.600 --> 00:04:29.480
She is Su Hua!

00:04:30.199 --> 00:04:31.279
I saw the scar on her face.

00:04:31.480 --> 00:04:32.360
There was a scar!

00:04:32.720 --> 00:04:33.800
She is Su Hua!

00:04:33.920 --> 00:04:34.680
Impossible.

00:04:35.079 --> 00:04:36.480
Su Hua is already dead.

00:04:37.040 --> 00:04:38.000
Xiao Ye,

00:04:38.480 --> 00:04:39.759
come look at me.

00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:42.240
Am I a human or a ghost?

00:04:47.160 --> 00:04:48.279
She is not Su Hua.

00:04:48.879 --> 00:04:49.759
Not Su Hua!

00:04:50.480 --> 00:04:51.560
I've heard that

00:04:51.959 --> 00:04:53.360
when people fall ill,

00:04:54.160 --> 00:04:56.079
those they once harmed

00:04:56.480 --> 00:04:58.160
turn into vengeful spirits

00:04:58.720 --> 00:04:59.759
to possess them

00:05:00.959 --> 00:05:02.120
and drain their life.

00:05:03.480 --> 00:05:04.399
Second Master,

00:05:05.079 --> 00:05:07.480
perhaps you committed
too many wrongs before,

00:05:08.240 --> 00:05:09.560
and now you face retribution.

00:05:13.800 --> 00:05:15.000
No, Mother! No!

00:05:15.040 --> 00:05:15.480
No!

00:05:16.040 --> 00:05:17.079
She is Su Hua!

00:05:17.360 --> 00:05:18.319
She is Su Hua!

00:05:18.959 --> 00:05:19.319
She...

00:05:20.120 --> 00:05:22.079
She is Su Hua! She is that woman!

00:05:22.279 --> 00:05:22.920
She...

00:05:23.040 --> 00:05:24.160
She must be in disguise.

00:05:24.360 --> 00:05:25.160
This is her disguise!

00:05:30.040 --> 00:05:30.759
Xiao Yun!

00:05:31.439 --> 00:05:32.839
After all these years,

00:05:33.079 --> 00:05:34.959
you still love her.
She became a ghost...

00:05:34.959 --> 00:05:35.759
Silence!

00:05:38.279 --> 00:05:39.120
She is Su Hua!

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:41.160
She has come as a ghost to haunt you!

00:05:41.160 --> 00:05:42.360
She has come for you!

00:05:43.639 --> 00:05:44.720
She will drain you dry!

00:05:44.879 --> 00:05:46.240
She will drain you dry!

00:05:47.079 --> 00:05:48.240
Who is the ghost here?

00:05:51.560 --> 00:05:52.680
What ghost?

00:05:52.759 --> 00:05:54.240
There are no ghosts here.

00:05:54.519 --> 00:05:56.680
Just children making mischief.

00:05:57.920 --> 00:05:58.879
Mother!

00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:00.319
You have to believe me!

00:06:00.319 --> 00:06:00.839
She really is...

00:06:00.879 --> 00:06:01.480
Ye!

00:06:03.360 --> 00:06:04.279
Your Highness.

00:06:04.759 --> 00:06:06.439
This useless son of mine

00:06:06.439 --> 00:06:08.720
had a nightmare last night
and spoke nonsense.

00:06:09.759 --> 00:06:10.959
I beg your forgiveness.

00:06:11.439 --> 00:06:13.560
Did Your Highness rest well?

00:06:14.079 --> 00:06:15.000
Very well.

00:06:15.519 --> 00:06:17.279
This authentic piece is truly rare.

00:06:18.079 --> 00:06:21.120
I never thought it would appear here.

00:06:30.040 --> 00:06:32.000
Xiao Lian, are you ready?

00:07:42.759 --> 00:07:43.319
General.

00:07:45.360 --> 00:07:47.920
Both the young lady's face

00:07:48.240 --> 00:07:49.279
and the real person are here.

00:07:50.680 --> 00:07:53.279
Which one will the General choose?

00:07:57.079 --> 00:07:58.439
It is only because I haven't seen you

00:07:59.040 --> 00:07:59.720
that I...

00:08:02.759 --> 00:08:03.959
The only one I want is you.

00:08:05.439 --> 00:08:06.639
No matter which face it is.

00:08:07.680 --> 00:08:09.480
I know, I understand.

00:08:10.319 --> 00:08:12.240
Xiao Lian was teasing you.
Don't mind her.

00:08:21.319 --> 00:08:22.240
(Spirit tablet of dear friend Su Hua)
Let's talk business.

00:08:23.560 --> 00:08:24.800
Since Xiao Ye

00:08:25.240 --> 00:08:27.279
is so terrified of Su Hua's face...

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:32.360
Let's go big.

00:08:33.720 --> 00:08:35.960
Xiao Lian, I'll be counting on you next.

00:08:36.120 --> 00:08:38.559
Make sure Xiao Ye
has no way to fight back.

00:08:39.799 --> 00:08:40.600
All right.

00:08:50.399 --> 00:08:51.480
Do you think

00:08:52.159 --> 00:08:54.120
Xiao Lian's disguise
will make Xiao Ye tell the truth?

00:08:55.480 --> 00:08:56.279
What?

00:08:56.759 --> 00:08:57.759
You don't believe me?

00:08:58.320 --> 00:08:59.840
Of course I believe you.

00:09:03.480 --> 00:09:04.960
But using Xiao Lian

00:09:05.559 --> 00:09:06.879
to trick the Empress Dowager is risky.

00:09:07.360 --> 00:09:08.960
It could cost your head.

00:09:09.399 --> 00:09:10.840
If something really happens to me,

00:09:11.919 --> 00:09:13.320
I will never implicate you.

00:09:13.679 --> 00:09:14.480
Hua.

00:09:25.639 --> 00:09:26.320
Hua.

00:09:28.360 --> 00:09:29.759
You are my wife.

00:09:30.919 --> 00:09:33.639
Your wish is my wish.

00:09:34.759 --> 00:09:35.360
I want to face

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:36.559
all of this with you.

00:09:38.759 --> 00:09:39.840
But I always feel

00:09:40.600 --> 00:09:43.120
that your plans never include me.

00:09:47.360 --> 00:09:48.759
That's because you came too late.

00:09:53.600 --> 00:09:54.320
I'm sorry.

00:09:57.399 --> 00:09:58.799
Never say sorry again.

00:09:59.320 --> 00:10:01.039
I don't mean you were late saving me.

00:10:01.279 --> 00:10:03.159
The plan was set long ago.

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:05.039
There was simply no part for you.

00:10:07.320 --> 00:10:08.120
Just as well.

00:10:08.919 --> 00:10:10.960
Now you can watch this play carefully.

00:10:11.960 --> 00:10:13.240
See for yourself,

00:10:14.200 --> 00:10:16.000
if your dear Hua has grown up.

00:10:33.480 --> 00:10:34.480
Your Highness,

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:36.559
I brought you a handkerchief.

00:10:40.080 --> 00:10:40.879
Girl.

00:10:41.639 --> 00:10:43.360
How did you know I needed one?

00:10:44.320 --> 00:10:45.840
Did your mistress send it?

00:10:46.559 --> 00:10:49.360
No. I came on my own.

00:10:49.840 --> 00:10:52.559
I once read the story on this wall.

00:10:52.679 --> 00:10:54.039
I already cried once.

00:10:54.360 --> 00:10:57.159
I thought,
though Your Highness is a heroine,

00:10:57.799 --> 00:10:58.679
you might still

00:10:58.879 --> 00:11:01.240
grieve for the young lady in the tale.

00:11:03.960 --> 00:11:06.919
Girl, you have read
"Record by the West Window"?

00:11:07.279 --> 00:11:08.279
I have, several times.

00:11:08.919 --> 00:11:09.679
But,

00:11:10.039 --> 00:11:13.159
I think Liu Shuzhen's best work is not
"Record by the West Window",

00:11:13.639 --> 00:11:15.879
but "Lost Souls".

00:11:16.519 --> 00:11:17.519
Wonderful.

00:11:18.279 --> 00:11:20.759
It has been so long since
I've spoken about storybooks.

00:11:21.480 --> 00:11:23.759
Girl, what is your name?

00:11:24.360 --> 00:11:25.919
Would you come to the palace with me?

00:11:28.320 --> 00:11:29.919
If Your Highness is
willing to take me in,

00:11:30.039 --> 00:11:31.279
of course I am willing.

00:11:31.679 --> 00:11:32.559
I am Su Hua.

00:11:35.759 --> 00:11:36.919
Greetings, Your Highness.

00:11:39.480 --> 00:11:40.720
Xiao Lian, how did it go?

00:11:40.960 --> 00:11:42.639
The Empress Dowager agreed
to let me accompany her.

00:11:43.679 --> 00:11:45.919
Xiao Lian,
you must be extremely careful.

00:11:46.039 --> 00:11:47.279
If she finds out,

00:11:47.279 --> 00:11:48.360
we will be doomed.

00:11:50.440 --> 00:11:51.759
I see.

00:11:51.919 --> 00:11:53.559
You are merely asking for a servant.

00:11:54.120 --> 00:11:55.320
That is simple.

00:11:55.559 --> 00:11:56.559
Whichever girl you fancy,

00:11:56.639 --> 00:11:57.639
just take her.

00:11:57.840 --> 00:11:59.120
It's her honor.

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:01.120
And it's the honor
of the Xiao Residence.

00:12:01.679 --> 00:12:02.559
But I wonder,

00:12:02.919 --> 00:12:04.679
which girl could be so lucky

00:12:04.879 --> 00:12:06.120
as to catch your eye?

00:12:06.759 --> 00:12:08.720
A girl in white clothing.

00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:10.519
A small face,

00:12:10.879 --> 00:12:12.159
quite a neat appearance.

00:12:12.759 --> 00:12:13.919
Her name is Su Hua.

00:12:16.120 --> 00:12:17.039
What is her name?

00:12:18.039 --> 00:12:19.559
Her name is Su Hua.

00:12:21.559 --> 00:12:22.559
That is impossible.

00:12:23.240 --> 00:12:24.519
Absolutely impossible.

00:13:09.960 --> 00:13:11.320
Qing Yan, oh Qing Yan.

00:13:12.600 --> 00:13:14.799
You hide such a great secret
in the shed.

00:13:15.440 --> 00:13:17.120
It could cost your head.

00:13:35.679 --> 00:13:36.639
This is the girl.

00:13:39.360 --> 00:13:41.639
Raise your head and look at me.

00:13:49.120 --> 00:13:50.519
Whose household are you from?

00:13:51.759 --> 00:13:55.240
I serve Miss Qing Yan.

00:13:58.960 --> 00:13:59.840
Qing Yan?

00:14:01.879 --> 00:14:02.679
What is it?

00:14:03.519 --> 00:14:04.559
Would you want her to stay?

00:14:05.080 --> 00:14:06.120
Of course not.

00:14:25.360 --> 00:14:29.080
♪Mountains and rivers rise and fall♪

00:14:29.080 --> 00:14:32.280
♪The vast sea opens wide♪

00:14:33.280 --> 00:14:36.280
♪Thank you for staying with me♪

00:14:36.280 --> 00:14:40.360
♪To witness all the lights of the world♪

00:14:40.920 --> 00:14:45.120
♪I remember by the old tree in Qing Yan♪

00:14:45.720 --> 00:14:48.160
♪When we first met♪

00:14:48.800 --> 00:14:55.880
♪Looking back, no more words are needed♪

00:14:56.280 --> 00:15:00.760
♪You went left, I went right♪

00:15:00.760 --> 00:15:04.840
♪If we hadn't met,
there'd be nothing to seek♪

00:15:05.520 --> 00:15:09.160
♪In this long, dusty road of life♪

00:15:09.160 --> 00:15:12.760
♪Love and hate poured
in a single jar of wine♪

00:15:12.760 --> 00:15:16.640
♪Whose heart does love truly claim♪

00:15:16.640 --> 00:15:20.960
♪Yet it yields to just one greeting♪

00:15:21.800 --> 00:15:25.160
♪Gentle longing flows into the river♪

00:15:25.160 --> 00:15:30.960
♪When dreams break,
we will guard each other still♪